description:
Get ready for a festive music video adventure with Numberblocks, Alphablocks, Colourblocks, and Wonderblocks â€” teaming up with FIFTY FIFTY to make Christmas magical! âœ¨
In this special holiday sing-along, we count down the days, spell out festive words, and fill the world with red, green, and sparkling Christmas colours â€” all with easy-to-follow moves kids can copy at home.

ğŸ¶ In this video, kids will:
 â€¢ âœ… Practise counting (with Numberblocks 1â€“5 and a Christmas countdown!)
 â€¢ âœ… Hear and spot letters and simple words (with Alphablocks)
 â€¢ âœ… Learn Christmas colours like red, green, silver, and gold (with Colourblocks)
 â€¢ âœ… Join in with dance-along actions that build confidence and coordination

ğŸ Perfect for: preschool & early years learning, Christmas classroom time, cosy family screen time, and holiday parties!

Stream the song on your favourite music platforms: https://orcd.co/8q2jv5b

As seen on CBeebies! Watch full episodes on BBC iPlayer: https://bbc.in/2OLEvWf
Subscribe for more Alphablocks and Numberblocks: https://goo.gl/zknx9d

The Alphablocks are 26 living letters who discover that whenever they hold hands and make a word, something magical happens. With adventures, songs and silliness, itâ€™s tons of fun with words â€“ all built on a firm foundation of key phonics skills. Alphablocks is the hit CBeebies TV show thatâ€™s already helped hundreds of thousands of children to learn to read and will bring phonics to life for anyone wishing to learn how to spell in English.  

The Numberblocks are little blocks with big ideas, having a ton of number fun! Learn how to add, subtract and count in a fun and educational way using singular blocks to do basic maths sums. They play games and sing songs about how easy it is to count! Numberblocks is a hit CBeebies show that is teaching children around the world how to count with easy to more advanced levels of numeracy for children.
